    ["Scenario: Dividends of $500 declared. Closing entry?", "Debit Retained Earnings $500 and credit Dividends $500."],
    ["Why verify adjusting and closing entries?", "To ensure accuracy and completeness before preparing the post-closing trial balance."],
    ["Scenario: Accrued salaries of $1,200. Adjusting entry?", "Debit Salaries Expense $1,200 and credit Salaries Payable $1,200 to record unpaid wages."]
